frames.caption: A humanoid cat with white fur stands in front of a wooden door, illuminated by a warm lantern. The creature is dressed in rustic clothing and carries a sack over its shoulder, gazing thoughtfully at the door.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting where a humanoid cat character is standing outside a wooden building at night. The atmosphere is mysterious and slightly tense, with the warm glow of the lantern contrasting against the cool night air.

frames.caption: A humanoid white cat stands at a wooden door, gently knocking. The scene is set in a dimly lit, rustic environment, with a warm glow emanating from a lantern beside the door.
frames.description: The scene depicts a humanoid cat character in a serene, rural setting, approaching a wooden house at dusk. The character appears to be on a journey, suggested by the sack slung over its shoulder.
